<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>AP examination results are accepted in transfer for selected coursework. Students must successfully complete high school AP course(s) with a grade of C or better and achieve a score of 4 or better on the AP examination for transfer credit to be awarded. Credit for AP coursework is limited to 30 semester hours.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.mcphs.edu/academics/course-catalog" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

